      • getDynCodecPlugins

        public static java.util.Map<java.lang.String,ExtraPlugins.DynCodecInfos> getDynCodecPlugins(Context ctxt,
                                                                                            java.lang.String action)
        Retrieve all dynamic codec plugins available in the platform It will resolve for a given action available sip plugins
        参数:
        ctxt - Context of the application
        action - Action of the plugin to be resolved For example SipManager.ACTION_GET_EXTRA_CODECS, SipManager.ACTION_GET_VIDEO_PLUGIN
        返回:
        a map containing plugins infos and registrered component name as key
